OL,3,CUnions to press for winter fuel
OL,4,Callowance cut to be reversed
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fhas described the policy as "cruel"
OL,8,Fand has called on the Prime Minister
OL,9,Fto admit he made a "misstep".
OL,11,FShe has said: "The first thing Labour
OL,12,Fdoes is to take away the winter fuel
OL,13,Fallowance from the poorest in our
OL,14,Fsociety while they leave the
OL,15,Fwealthiest people pretty much
OL,16,Funtouched."
