OL,3,CUnions to press for winter fuel
OL,4,Callowance cut to be reversed
OL,6,FCWU officials will not be at Labour's
OL,7,Fconference on Wednesday as they are
OL,8,Fattending the funeral in Scotland of
OL,9,Fthe union's former assistant general
OL,10,Fsecretary Andy Kerr, who used to be on
OL,11,FLabour's national executive.
OL,13,FCWU general secretary Dave Ward told
OL,14,Fthe PA news agency that the union will
OL,15,Fcontinue to campaign for the policy to
OL,16,Fchange.
OL,18,F"We don't accept it is good
OL,19,Feconomics," he said.
