OL,3,CUnions to press for winter fuel
OL,4,Callowance cut to be reversed
OL,6,FThe motion being debated says that
OL,7,Fworkers and communities voted for
OL,8,Fchange, "not cuts to the winter fuel
OL,9,Fallowance".
OL,11,F"We need a vision where pensioners are
OL,12,Fnot the first to face a new wave of
OL,13,Fcuts and those that profited from
OL,14,Fdecades of deregulation finally help
OL,15,Fto rebuild Britain," it says.
