OL,3,CUnions to press for winter fuel
OL,4,Callowance cut to be reversed
OL,6,FThe motion calls for means testing of
OL,7,Fthe winter fuel allowance to be
OL,8,Freversed and for an end to fiscal
OL,9,Frules which prevent borrowing to
OL,10,Finvest, as well as the introduction of
OL,11,Fa wealth tax.
OL,13,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,14,Fin his conference speech on Tuesday
OL,15,Fthat he understood concern over the
OL,16,Fwinter fuel allowance but stressed
OL,17,Fthat stabilising the economy was the
OL,18,Ffirst step of a long-term plan,
OL,19,Fadding: "Every pensioner will be
OL,20,Fbetter off with Labour."
